import React from "react";
import { Container, Col, Row, Form, FormGroup, FormInput } from "shards-react";

import PageTitle from "../../components/common/PageTitle";

export default function UploadDietPlan() {
  return (
    <Container fluid className="main-content-container px-4 pb-4">
      <Row noGutters className="page-header py-4">
        <PageTitle
          sm="4"
          title="Upload Diet Plan"
          subtitle="Dashboard"
          className="text-sm-left"
        />
      </Row>
      <Col>
        <Form className="card">
          <CardHeader></CardHeader>
          <FormGroup>
            <label htmlFor="doc_title">Document Title</label>
            <FormInput 
              type="text"
              name="document_title"
              id="doc_title"
              size="lg"
              className="mb-3"
              placeholder="Document Title"
            />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <label>Document</label>

          </FormGroup>
        </Form>
      </Col>
    </Container>
  );
}
